coursing inside,

83
00:06:17,077 --> 00:06:19,346
and I can feel
everything connected

84
00:06:19,379 --> 00:06:21,648
throughout the entire tree.

85
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:27,488
I can do it.

86
00:06:27,521 --> 00:06:30,557
As long as I don’t go
against the tree’s guidance,

87
00:06:30,591 --> 00:06:31,625
i’ll be fine.

88
00:06:45,906 --> 00:06:47,875
Man: H-help!

89
00:06:47,908 --> 00:06:49,109
Gon: Eh?

90
00:06:49,142 --> 00:06:51,411
Man: Please, anybody,

91
00:06:51,445 --> 00:06:53,614
